# cloudflared/config.yml.template
# 部署時請將此檔案複製為 cloudflared/config.yml，並填入實際的 tunnel 名稱與 credentials 路徑。

tunnel: pest-backend
credentials-file: /Users/<your-username>/.cloudflared/pest-backend.json

ingress:
  - hostname: api.your-domain.com
    service: http://localhost:8000
  - service: http_status:404
